---
title: Calorie Smart Greek-Inspired Pork Chops with Lemony Roasted Potatoes and Feta Green Beans
description: All the familiar flavours of Greek cuisine are packed into this dinner! Garlicky pork, lemony roasted potatoes and feta green beans round out this weeknight winner, which is finished with a dollop of tzatziki, to boot!

